padding:1rem 2rem;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.15);\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.6rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;display:block;\">\u20b9XX Cr</span><span style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;display:block;margin-top:4px;\">Grants Available</span><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.5;letter-spacing:0.1em;\">DST / BIRAC Pipeline</span></div></div></div>"
