            "id": "34c6dea4",
            "elType": "widget",
            "settings": {
              "html": "<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:6rem;align-items:center;\">\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Why BMIIL</p>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.15;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">The <em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#C49A2A;\">right place</em><br><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">at the right time</strong></h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#4A5C78;max-width:520px;margin:0 0 2rem;\">India's healthcare innovation is concentrated in 5 cities. Tier-2 India \u2014 home to 800 million people \u2014 has no medtech infrastructure. BMIIL is built to change that, starting from Bareilly with a model designed to replicate across North India.</p>\n      <a href=\"/about/#vision\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;\">Read More</a>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1.2rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83c\udfe5</div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.4rem;\">Clinical Access</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Direct pipeline to BIU's multi-speciality hospital for problem identification and validation.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\u2697\ufe0f</div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.4rem;\">Lab Infrastructure</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Prototyping, biotech, and pharma labs across Medicine, Pharmacy, and Allied Health.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83d\udccb</div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.4rem;\">Regulatory Support</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">In-house guidance on CDSCO, FDA, AYUSH, and WHO compliance pathways.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;padding:1.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><div style=\"font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.8rem;\">\ud83c\udf3f</div><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.4rem;\">Ayurveda + MedTech</h4><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Unique fusion track \u2014 scientifically validating traditional medicine with modern tools.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
