            "id": "14fdfc17",
            "elType": "widget",
            "settings": {
              "html": "<div style=\"background:#EDE8DE;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\">\n    <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Our Edge</p>\n    <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.15;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 3.5rem;\"><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#C49A2A;\">Six reasons</em> to build<br><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">your startup here</strong></h2>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.2;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">01</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Tier-2 India Advantage</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Lower burn, massive patient access, authentic problem statements from an underserved healthcare market that investors are increasingly watching.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.2;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">02</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Captive Clinical Pipeline</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Direct access to BIU's teaching hospital gives startups immediate problem identification, validation partners, and pilot environments.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.2;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">03</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Regulatory Navigation</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">In-house mentors experienced in CDSCO, FDA, AYUSH, and WHO pathways \u2014 reducing time-to-compliance by months.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.2;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">04</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">The Ayurveda Angle</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">No other medtech incubator in India offers a credible, evidence-based Ayurveda + technology fusion track backed by university research.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.2;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">05</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Grant Ecosystem Access</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Active pipeline to DST, BIRAC, Startup India, and international grants \u2014 our team actively facilitates applications and submissions.</p></div><div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:3.5rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.2;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">06</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Multidisciplinary Faculty</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">200+ researchers across Medicine, Pharmacy, Biotech, Dental and Allied Health available as subject matter experts and co-innovators.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
